Package: detectconf
Title: Detection Confidence for Invasive Species Records from GBIF
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Eva", "Benavides Rios",
           email = "eva.benavides.rios@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A prototype framework for interpreting novel invasion signals
    in GBIF occurrence records. DetectConf models where the observation
    system would be expected to detect a species if it were present,
    producing a reliability map of the observation system itself rather
    than a habitat suitability surface.
